cs.IOT, cs.DC, cs.SE, cs.DB, cs.AI 

The paper discusses the Internet of Things (IoT) paradigm and its merging with Cloud Computing, which falls under the domain of IoT. Therefore, cs.IOT is the most likely sub-category. The paper also discusses the search and selection of sensors, which involves data management and decision-making, making cs.DC and cs.DB likely sub-categories. The paper also mentions the use of multi-criteria decision analysis, which falls under the domain of Artificial Intelligence, making cs.AI a likely sub-category. Finally, the paper discusses the quality of selection presented by these methods, which involves software engineering principles, making cs.SE a possible sub-category.
